{"word":"Gezer","slug":"gezer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gezer</b> <a href=\"#/H1507\">H1507</a> <br/> Called also Gazer, Gazara, Gazera, and Gob. A Canaanitish royal city.<br/> King of, defeats Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=33'>Jos 10:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=12'>Jos 12:12</a><br/> Canaanites not all expelled from, but made to pay tribute<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=10'>Jos 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=29'>Jdg 1:29</a><br/> Allotted to Ephraim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=3'>Jos 16:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=16&verse=10'>Jos 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=28'>1Ch 7:28</a><br/> Assigned to Levites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=21'>Jos 21:21</a><br/> Battle with Philistines at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=4'>1Ch 20:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=18'>2Sa 21:18</a><br/> Smitten by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=8'>1Sa 27:8</a><br/> Fortified by Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=17'>1Ki 9:17</a>"}]}